705702f-a.title: Brooklyn: Meserole Street - Bushwick Avenue
705702f-a.text:
Meserole Street, west from Bushwick Ave. The restaurant at the left,
is on Bushwick Ave. At the extreme right, is a alight view of P.S. No. 196.
October 25, 1934.
P. L. Sperr.
